UNIT 1 6 1 3 1
sump 1.0000 0.00001 1 6 1 7 1 8
DFIX 1.47 0.001 C1 N1 C2 N2 C3 N3
DFIX 2.93 0.1 H11 H16 H21 H26 H31 H36
SADI 0.01 H11 H14 H11 H15
